{
  "stem": "25423.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as I was reasonably resourceful, I became an instructor of the Red Cross-- first aid because it was non-political.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as a senior instructor, eventually, of the Red Cross, I was meshed into the Civil Defense System, which was organized by the Russian military.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I became, essentially, part of the mechanism and out of the clutches of the consort.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Go to school in the [NON-ENGLISH], 10 year program.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's the name of the school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- previously a Jewish school, so most of the kids were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was gymnasium, which was transformed into a Soviet school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I spent about until 2 o'clock or 3 o'clock at school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from then on, I had to go to work in my activities as an instructor of the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Other kids-- this time, boys and girls because the Soviets have commingled a Jewish gymnasium for girls with boys and divided the students so that the classes were coeducation.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we were quite well aware of what was going on in the rest of Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that there's a persecution of Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were not aware of the brutality or anything which would lead us to think that there's an extermination program.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were certainly oppressed by the Soviets, but not to the same extent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a semblance of normal life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after the first year under Soviet occupation, the supply situation has improved somewhat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- and life was more normal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we were annexed to the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So Lwow became a Soviet administrators' center.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, on the other hand, this was the start of major arrests and deportations.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I wasn't interested in Hebrew studies before the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I didn't go out of my way to resume it under the Soviet occupation.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
